entries.journal_entry_description: It's time for you to acquire an appropriate lightsaber and crystal. Nos'lyn will show you the way.
entries.task00_comm_message_text: You seem to be progressing well along the path. It is time to acquire the weapon unique to those steeped in the Force. Find a crystal from a cave on Naboo. Instructions will be in your journal.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Nos'lyn sent you a message: You seem to be progressing well along the path. It is time to acquire the weapon unique to those steeped in the Force. Find a crystal from a cave on Naboo.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Nos'lyn wants you to go to a cave on Naboo to find a suitable crystal for yourself.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: You need to find a crystal that is appropriate for you. Search for one among the crystal formations.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: The crystal that you seek is here. None that you have found so far have worked. Search your feelings and find your crystal.
entries.task05_comm_message_text: Keep that crystal safe and hidden. You will need to tune it and then you can put it into your lightsaber. Sol Windtide has a jedi's saber for you.
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: Nos'lyn sent you another message: Keep that crystal safe and hidden. You will need to tune it and then you can put it into your lightsaber. Sol Windtide has a jedi's saber for you.
entries.task06_journal_entry_description: Return to Tatooine and talk to Sol Windtide.
